    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just really stressed about the insomnia so i'd rather deal with a little extra drowsiness than stay up all night again. if i just keep it to one small glass of wine and stick to my prescribed dose, it shouldn't be an issue, right? like, it's not going to actually stop my breathing if it's just a small amount? i'd rather just have a way to make sure it actually works.",
